Package: MCPR
Type: Package
Title: MCPR: Model Context Protocol Implementation for R Session Integration
Version: 0.9.03
Authors@R: 
    person("Santiago", "Cano-Muniz", , "tisalon@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Santiago Cano-Muniz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Santiago Cano-Muniz <tisalon@outlook.com>
Description: Provides a robust implementation of the Model Context Protocol (MCP) 
    for R, bridging the execution model gap between AI coding assistants and 
    interactive R workflows. Transforms AI-R interaction from stateless script 
    execution to collaborative session participation through JSON-RPC 2.0 
    communication over nanonext sockets. Core capabilities include persistent 
    workspace management, intelligent graphics rendering with token optimization, 
    comprehensive session introspection, and multi-session coordination. 
    Designed with principles of modularity, cross-platform compatibility, and 
    enterprise-grade reliability. Integrates seamlessly with existing R workflows 
    while providing standardized tool interfaces for AI agent communication. 
    Suitable for development environments requiring stateful AI assistance and 
    collaborative analytical workflows.
